{ [ identification, verb.cognition:identify4,+ ] identity,@ (the attribution to yourself (consciously or unconsciously) of the characteristics of another person (or group of persons)) }
{ [ personhood, noun.Tops:person,+ ] identity,@ (being a person; "finding her own personhood as a campus activist") }
